OL,3,CThe children in care left homeless
OL,4,Cafter 'shocking' failure by social
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThree children under the care of
OL,8,Fsocial services in Birmingham were
OL,9,Fleft homeless for five months, as ITV
OL,10,FNews' Investigation Editor Daniel
OL,11,FHewitt reports
OL,13,FThree children under the care of
OL,14,Fsocial services in Birmingham were
OL,15,Fleft homeless for five months, an ITV
OL,16,FNews investigation has uncovered.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/31
