OL,3,CThe children in care left homeless
OL,4,Cafter 'shocking' failure by social
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThe three siblings, who are not yet
OL,8,Fteenagers, are subject to a local
OL,9,Fauthority care order, which means
OL,10,FBirmingham City Council have parental
OL,11,Fresponsibility for their wellbeing.
OL,13,FYet they were forced to share beds in
OL,14,Fbudget hotel rooms and sofa-surf
OL,15,Facross the city for several months.
OL,17,FAfter becoming homeless in August last
OL,18,Fyear, a social worker didn't visit the
OL,19,Fchildren for almost eight weeks.
