OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThe man who led the national
OL,8,Findependent review into children's
OL,9,Fsocial care in England, Josh
OL,10,FMacAlister, has told ITV News it is
OL,11,Fone of the most "shocking" and
OL,12,F"extreme" cases he has seen.
OL,14,FBirmingham City council has admitted
OL,15,Fit did not move quickly enough to help
OL,16,Fthe children.
OL,18,FThe three children, whose identities
OL,19,Fwe are protecting, were removed from
OL,20,Ftheir birth mother's care six years
OL,21,Fago.
