OL,7,FTheir grandmother, Sonia, immediately
OL,8,Fapplied to look after them and nine
OL,9,Fmonths later she was named as their
OL,10,Ffoster carer, with the council
OL,11,Fretaining ultimate parental
OL,12,Fresponsibility.
OL,14,FIn February 2023, Sonia was handed a
OL,15,Fno-fault eviction in the house she
OL,16,Frented from a private landlord.
