OL,4,Cafter 'shocking' failure by social
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FUnable to find anywhere else
OL,8,Faffordable on her foster carer's
OL,9,Fallowance, she notified social
OL,10,Fservices that the family needed a
OL,11,Fplace to live.
OL,13,FDespite continuous reassurances the
OL,14,Ffamily wouldn't become homeless, 16
OL,15,Fmonths later and a failed attempt to
OL,16,Foverturn the eviction in court, Sonia,
OL,17,Fher three grandchildren and her 16-
OL,18,Fyear-old son, were evicted with no
OL,19,Fwere to go.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/31
