OL,7,F"On the day we had to get out the
OL,8,Fproperty... they said they had nowhere
OL,9,Ffor us," Sonia said.
OL,11,F"I literally sat in the car, crying.
OL,12,FHow could the system allow the three
OL,13,Fchildren under a care order to be
OL,14,Fhomeless?"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/31
