OL,7,FAfter spending hours in her car, they
OL,8,Fwere eventually offered a temporary
OL,9,Froom in a budget hotel. They were then
OL,10,Fmoved to another budget hotel in the
OL,11,Fcity centre, where the children were
OL,12,Fforced to share beds and a hotel room
OL,13,Fwith Sonia.
OL,15,FNo risk assessment or review was
OL,16,Fcarried out of any of the properties
OL,17,Fthe children were placed in, and Sonia
OL,18,Fsays it took eight weeks for the
OL,19,Fchildren's social worker to visit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/31
