OL,7,FDespite being responsible for the
OL,8,Fchildren's whereabouts and welfare,
OL,9,FSonia says social services began
OL,10,Fignoring her pleas for help.
OL,12,F"Social services are meant to be
OL,13,Fhelping. We're meant to be doing this
OL,14,Fas joint effort. And they've literally
OL,15,Fdone nothing to help us.
OL,17,F"They've got to the stage now where
OL,18,Fthey don't even bother to reply back
OL,19,Fto me," she says.
