OL,7,FWe met Sonia and the children in
OL,8,FAugust in their tiny, temporary hotel
OL,9,Froom on a busy main road in the city.
OL,11,FNo fridge, no internet, their clothes
OL,12,Fand possessions in bags, it was
OL,13,Fclearly not suitable for young,
OL,14,Fvulnerable children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/31
