OL,7,FThen, while we were filming with
OL,8,FSonia, her mobile phone began to ring.
OL,9,FIt was the council's housing
OL,10,Fdepartment, telling Sonia their hotel
OL,11,Fbooking was being cancelled and they
OL,12,Fwould be moving again that same day to
OL,13,Fdifferent temporary accommodation.
OL,15,F"Can I ask what it is, a hotel, flats?"
OL,17,F"A homeless centre," came the reply
OL,18,Ffrom the call-handler.
OL,20,FSonia asked if it had a shared kitchen.
