OL,7,F"I would presume so yes," she was told.
OL,9,F"I have three children under a care
OL,10,Forder, and if it is shared kitchen,
OL,11,Fwith strangers, isn't that a
OL,12,Fsafeguarding issue?" Sonia asked,
OL,13,Fconcerned that they simply didn't know
OL,14,Fenough about the homeless centre to
OL,15,Faccept the offer.
OL,17,FThe call-handler was silent.
