OL,7,FThe call ended, and Sonia received a
OL,8,Ftext message confirming their hotel
OL,9,Fstay would be cancelled and they would
OL,10,Fhave to leave by the next morning.
OL,12,FSonia had not even had chance to visit
OL,13,Fthe homeless centre or speak to anyone
OL,14,Ffrom social services about its
OL,15,Fsuitability for the children.
OL,17,FI asked Sonia if she had received any
OL,18,Fmessage or call from social services -
OL,19,Fshe hadn't.
