OL,7,FWhile she then called the social
OL,8,Fworker to seek answers, I looked up
OL,9,Fthe address Sonia had been told she
OL,10,Fhad no choice but to accept.
OL,12,FA local newspaper had written an
OL,13,Farticle about families living at the
OL,14,Fcentre, who complained of infestations
OL,15,Fof rats and cockroaches, and anti-
OL,16,Fsocial behaviour and drug use on the
OL,17,Fpremises.
