OL,7,FReviews of the accommodation were
OL,8,Fscathing, also talking of poor
OL,9,Fconditions and vermin, and that
OL,10,Fresidents were left without heating
OL,11,Fand hot water for weeks on end.
OL,13,FSonia was understandably worried, and
OL,14,Fincreasingly anxious.
OL,16,FWith her bags packed, we left the
OL,17,Fhotel and drove across Birmingham to
OL,18,Fthe homeless centre with Sonia and the
OL,19,Fchildren.
