OL,7,FThe first thing we saw outside the
OL,8,Fmetal, barbed railings that surrounded
OL,9,Fthe complex was piles and piles of
OL,10,Frubbish, discarded clothes and shoes,
OL,11,Fand food. You can see why there had
OL,12,Fbeen reports of a rodent problem.
OL,14,FSonia was visibly shaken. She had got
OL,15,Fhold of her social worker, who
OL,16,Fconfirmed no risk assessment or
OL,17,Finspection had been carried out on the
OL,18,Fproperty to see if it was safe or
OL,19,Fsuitable for the children under a care
OL,20,Forder.
