OL,7,FSonia's biggest concern was who else
OL,8,Fwas living at the accommodation.
OL,10,FThe children's birth mother is legally
OL,11,Fnot allowed any contact with them, but
OL,12,Fthe last time Sonia was aware of her
OL,13,Fwhereabouts, she was in temporary
OL,14,Faccommodation in Birmingham.
OL,16,F"Their mum could be in there. It's
OL,17,Fjust a risk issue," she tells me.
OL,19,F"I just think the system is completely
OL,20,Fand utterly wrong."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/31
