OL,7,FBy turning down the accommodation,
OL,8,FSonia was told she was making herself
OL,9,Fintentionally homeless and would not
OL,10,Fbe offered any alternative place to
OL,11,Fstay. By morning, they would be on the
OL,12,Fstreets.
OL,14,F"The situation she's been put in
OL,15,Fthere, is shocking and shouldn't
OL,16,Fhappen," Josh MacAlister told ITV News
OL,18,FWe took our findings to Josh
OL,19,FMacAlister, who in 2022 led the
OL,20,Fnational independent review into
OL,21,Fchildren's social care.
