OL,7,F"This is one of the more extreme
OL,8,Fcases," he says.
OL,10,F"But the themes of it are really
OL,11,Fcommon across the care system.
OL,13,F"What's so upsetting about this
OL,14,Fsituation is that Sonia has done
OL,15,Feverything right. She's stepped into
OL,16,Fthat incredibly difficult situation to
OL,17,Flook after her three grandchildren.
OL,18,FThe situation she's been put into is
OL,19,Fshocking and shouldn't happen.
