OL,7,F"We should ` the system, the state `
OL,8,Fshould be finding every way possible
OL,9,Fto say Sonia you're doing an amazing
OL,10,Fthing here ` how can we help?
OL,12,F"If the situation broke down, those
OL,13,Fkids might enter the care system,
OL,14,Fwhere they may end up not being placed
OL,15,Fin a home together. They might be
OL,16,Fseparated, which would be even more
OL,17,Fdifficult for them.
OL,19,F"These are the kind of situations that
OL,20,Fshould be a wake-up call for the care
OL,21,Fsystem."
