OL,13,Fhomeless centre on safety grounds, by
OL,14,FOctober they still hadn't found
OL,15,Fanywhere to live.
OL,17,FThey had been homeless for four
OL,18,Fmonths. Their only option after being
OL,19,Fevicted from the hotel was to stay
