OL,3,CThe children in care left homeless
OL,4,Cafter 'shocking' failure by social
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FSonia, her own 16-year-old son and the
OL,8,Fthree grandchildren were squeezed into
OL,9,Fa small, two-bedroom bungalow.
OL,11,FSix of them sharing two rooms.
OL,13,F"I share the bed with one of the
OL,14,Fchildren, and the other child sleeps
OL,15,Fon the airbed on the floor," Sonia
OL,16,Fsays, as she shows us around one of
OL,17,Fthe cramped rooms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/31
