OL,3,CThe children in care left homeless
OL,4,Cafter 'shocking' failure by social
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"And one of the children sleeps in
OL,8,Fhere with my mum." The other bedroom
OL,9,Fis also full - of bedding, belongings
OL,10,Fand bags,
OL,12,FSonia's son is sleeping on the living
OL,13,Froom sofa.
OL,15,FI ask her if what she and her family
OL,16,Fhas been through is neglect.
OL,18,F"Yes," she says. "Definitely."
