OL,3,CThe children in care left homeless
OL,4,Cafter 'shocking' failure by social
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"It's just heartbreaking because most
OL,8,Fnights when I pick the children up
OL,9,Ffrom school the first thing they ask
OL,10,Fme is 'have you found us a house?' and
OL,11,FI have to say no.
OL,13,F"I just want a smile on their faces to
OL,14,Fbe able to say, yes, we've got a
OL,15,Fhouse. We've got somewhere to live
OL,16,Fnow."
