OL,3,CThe children in care left homeless
OL,4,Cafter 'shocking' failure by social
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FBirmingham City Council declared
OL,8,Fitself bankrupt in September 2023.
OL,9,FBetween 2024 and 2026 the council had
OL,10,Fannounced budget cuts of more than
OL,11,F#100 million for children and families
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,FA crisis in social care is colliding
OL,15,Fwith a housing crisis in the city.
OL,16,FBirmingham has the third highest rate
OL,17,Fof homelessness in England, with more
OL,18,Fthan 16,000 households in temporary
OL,19,Faccommodation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G25/31
