OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FIn mid-November, five months after
OL,8,Fbeing made homeless and 19 months
OL,9,Fsince Sonia first informed social
OL,10,Fservices of the eviction notice, the
OL,11,Fcouncil helped to secure the family a
OL,12,Fthree-bedroom property in the private
OL,13,Frental sector.
OL,15,FWe took our findings to Birmingham
OL,16,FCity Council.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G26/31
