OL,4,Cafter 'shocking' failure by social
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FJames Thomas, Birmingham Children's
OL,8,FTrust Chief Executive, said: "We have
OL,9,Fbeen supporting Sonia with her housing
OL,10,Fneeds but recognise that we could have
OL,11,Ftaken greater steps to resolve the
OL,12,Fsituation more quickly for her and the
OL,13,Fchildren.
OL,15,F"We plan to reflect on the learning
OL,16,Ffrom this case to identify potential
OL,17,Fimprovements we can make to our
OL,18,Fpractice."
