OL,7,FCouncillor Jayne Francis, Cabinet
OL,8,FMember for Housing and Homelessness,
OL,9,Fsaid the city was in the grips of a
OL,10,Fhousing crisis that needed government
OL,11,Fintervention.
OL,13,F"The national housing crisis is
OL,14,Fcausing unprecedented demand for
OL,15,Faccommodation in Birmingham.
OL,16,FCurrently, we have around 25,000
OL,17,Fhouseholds on our housing register
OL,18,Fseeking a home.
