OL,3,CThe children in care left homeless
OL,4,Cafter 'shocking' failure by social
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"We are doing all we can to build new
OL,8,Fhomes so that families do not have to
OL,9,Fendure difficult circumstances like
OL,10,Fthis, but councils at present, cannot
OL,11,Fkeep pace with the demand to build new
OL,12,Fcouncil homes without government
OL,13,Fintervention. We will work with the
OL,14,Fgovernment to do all we can to build
OL,15,Fmore.
OL,17,F"I am glad that the family has managed
OL,18,Fto secure a suitable new home in the
OL,19,Fprivate rented sector with the help of
OL,20,FBirmingham City Council."
