OL,7,FCouncillor Francis added that the
OL,8,Fhomeless centre the family were
OL,9,Foffered "represents good quality
OL,10,Fhousing provision for those requiring
OL,11,Ftemporary accommodation in the city"
OL,12,Fwith "site security operating on a
OL,13,Fround-the-clock basis, as well as
OL,14,Fcleaning, maintenance and support
OL,15,Fteams."
OL,17,FReacting to the statements, Sonia told
OL,18,Fus she is "very upset" the council has
OL,19,Fnot apologised for the situation the
OL,20,Ffamily were put through.
