OL,7,FShe said the family has not received
OL,8,Fany contact from the council to
OL,9,Fdirectly apologise to her or the
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,F"The experience has been
OL,13,Fhorrendous...it can only be described
OL,14,Fas a nightmare," she said.
OL,16,F"They have no idea whatsoever what me
OL,17,Fand the children had to go through."
